name: EventDamage
description: This event is fired when the player takes damage from any source.
overview: Fires when the player takes damage from any source. The `attacker` field is deprecated and may be null on servers. The `source` field is deprecated and may not be reliable on servers. The `change` field is negative for damage events. Not cancellable.

methods.name: toString
methods.description: Returns a string representation of the event object.
